    Enable GitHub's dependabot for automatic dependency updates (#244)
    
    * Enable dependabot for automatic dep updates
    
    Dependabot scans dependencies daily for updates and will open PRs
    to upgrade the deps (which will then run through CI), if newer
    versions are published.
    
    For details, see
    https://docs.github.com/en/github/administering-a-repository/about-github-dependabot-version-updates
    
    Signed-off-by: Shon Feder <shon@informal.systems>
    
    * Set the interval to weekly

